# ChatBot App (Laravel 12 + OAuth2 + Passport)

This is a Laravel 12-based ChatBot application built for a recruitment test. It includes OAuth2 authentication using Laravel Passport, multi-factor authentication (MFA), CRUD operations, a follow-up module, and real-time chat features.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Laravel Passport (OAuth2) authentication
- ✅ Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) via Email
- ✅ CRUD for Customers, Chat Messages, and Follow-Ups
- ✅ ChatBot integration
- ✅ Real-time user-to-user chat (if implemented)
- ✅ Google/Facebook login ready (via Laravel Socialite)
- ✅ AdminLTE dashboard UI

---

## 🛠️ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sachin8800/chatbot-app.git
cd chatbot-app
1 composer install
2 npm install && npm run build
3 cp .env.example .env
4 php artisan key:generate
5 php artisan migrate
6 php artisan passport:install
You can run all Laravel tests using:
7 php artisan test
🔐 OAuth2 Access
Use Laravel Passport to generate personal access tokens or connect using Postman with the Authorization: Bearer {token} header.
